{"tid":2019878,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"東江水含致癌物  陳茂波指不損健康","createTime":"2020-05-16T14:56:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T15:12:39.000Z","uid":212274,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2ce73316de0811d79a874813bec264bb14deaa32","tid":2019878,"uid":212274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T14:56:34.000Z","msg":"2016-01-07<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】綠色和平早前在多個水塘驗出含有害致癌物質全氟化合物。發展局昨承認，水務署自2012年起的定期測驗已發現，輸港東江水的全氟化合物含量略高，但水平仍遠低於美國及英國安全標準。而內地亦正加強監控及加建污水處理設施，防止東江水受污染。<br />\n發展局長陳茂波昨在立會回覆議員提問時表示，水務署由2012年起的環境基線水平調查，開始測驗食水內兩種全氟化合物含量，包括全氟辛烷磺酸（Perfluorooctane Sulphonate，PFOS）及全氟辛酸銨（Perfluorooctanoic Acid，PFOA）<br />\n<br />\n結果顯示，接收東江水的木湖抽水站，PFOS及PFOA含量最高，而儲存東江水的船灣淡水湖、萬宜水庫、大欖涌水塘的PFOS含量，亦比只收集雨水的石壁水塘高，最多相差達5倍。<br />\n在濾水廠抽取的經處理食水樣本，亦驗出含PFOS及PFOA，去年測驗結果是每公升食水分別含低於4.6納克PFOS，及低於1.5納克PFOA。<br />\n陳茂波指，水務署是以世衞《飲用水水質準則》作供水水質目標，但世衞沒就全氟化合物訂定準則。<br />\n而美國環保局訂定的暫定建議值，PFOA為每公升400納克，PFOS為每公升200納克；英國飲用水監督機構的指引準則值PFOA和PFOS同為每公升300納克。本港食水PFOA和PFOS含量遠低於上述兩個安全標準，因此不會對健康構成影響。<br />\n對於深圳曾因暴雨排洪，令沙灣河受肥料污染的污水流入輸港的深圳水庫，陳茂波表示港深雙方已設立通報機制，當深圳需排洪時，水務署會增加抽驗輸港東江水次數，若發現水質變差，會在過濾廠加強處理。<br />\n■記者麥志榮<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20160107/large/a0803a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20160107%2Flarge%2Fa0803a.gif&h=2f1f4b0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20160107/19441986\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20160107%2F19441986&d=IqGrl%2FmL2I6%2Fp6gKwmVM%2BQXckNDuUEQQ0Md4EdtPbyE%3D&h=fc6f1ecb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20160107%2F19441986&h=ff869702\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20160107/19441986</a>"},{"pid":"2cb87915b25d4477fae7eedc3b6e3089a2f0d20d","tid":2019878,"uid":212274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T14:57:18.000Z","msg":"有冇人記得呢件事最後有無人跟進"},{"pid":"4949e121ac434945ed74944398688c374bba6c9a","tid":2019878,"uid":249924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T14:58:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0afe7a0e55462f04077a18017b26274fca6a3778","tid":2019878,"uid":522,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T14:59:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OJ2WvPs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOJ2WvPs.jpg&h=c70c42b4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bf4d372241ae6a1a1d57c4c59b65812f0e299ccc","tid":2019878,"uid":212274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T14:59:55.000Z","msg":"點解最後可以不了了知"},{"pid":"62cd33b23ad643a094eb17d07465e22a0ec0301a","tid":2019878,"uid":98163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T15:00:10.000Z","msg":"有害氣體無害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"563a5adbf2920b31fcdea5bb8e26db9c60148edf","tid":2019878,"uid":99420,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T15:04:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f0850c50a2613c767165e52836ceace378ca16c4","tid":2019878,"uid":65089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T15:07:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a83ad1bfba9bdfbe00ceed944ad421b19743ee4a","tid":2019878,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf4d372241ae6a1a1d57c4c59b65812f0e299ccc","tid":2019878,"uid":212274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-